#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:387
msgid ""
"Select a :guilabel:`Field To Clean` from the model to assign to an action."
msgstr "حدد :guilabel:`الحقل المراد تنظيفه` من النموذج لتعيينه إلى إجراء."

