"United States: `800 555-0101` :icon:`fa-long-arrow-right` `+1 800-555-0101`"
msgstr ""
"الولايات المتحدة: `800 555-0101` :icon:`fa-long-arrow-right` `+1 800-555-0101`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:418
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Scrap HTML` converts :abbr:`HTML (HyperText Markup Language)` to "
